OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry. Then the rest of the
OL,7,Fnight will be mainly dry and often
OL,8,Fcloudy, a few showers possible across
OL,9,FOrkney later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA mainly cloudy day with
OL,12,Foccasional showers, some misty low
OL,13,Fcloud across Shetland. Becoming breezy
OL,14,Facross Orkney.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,17,Fstart Saturday before outbreaks of
OL,18,Frain spread east in the afternoon and
OL,19,Fevening. Showery rain on Sunday before
OL,20,Fit turns drier on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
